{"id": "1438800071977078814", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "感谢各位守密人的支持！\n《忘却前夜》OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响 已发布，欢迎收听、下载及分享。\n如果有基于OST的二次创作，也欢迎分享给我们！（二创请遵照同人规则，OST内容请勿商用）\n\n**忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响**\n你用一千颗橡果交换了一个来自异界的故事。\n一个关于英雄与魔神，守望与坚持的故事。\n一个关于无奈与不舍，旧朋友与新朋友的故事。\n一个曾经来过的故事。\n\n作曲：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\n规划：B.I.A.V. Studio\n\n——◆——◆—— ◆◆◆ ——◆——◆——\n\nThank you for your support!\n\nMorimens OST: \"My Turn EP: The Echo of Cosmic Tavern\" was released today. \nWelcome everyone to listen, download and share. If you have secondary creations based on the OST, please also share them with us!\n (Please follow the rules of the fandom for secondary creations, and do not use the OST content for commercial purposes)\n\n**Morimens OST: My Turn EP: The Echo of Cosmic Tavern**\nYou exchanged 1000 acorns for a story from another world.\nA story of heroes and the demon god, of watching and perseverance.\nA story of helplessness and reluctance, of old friends and new.\nA story that once was.\n\nComposer：F.R.K./ B.I.A.V. Studio\nPlanning：B.I.A.V. Studio", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T07:57:48.772000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "👍", "emoji_id": null, "count": 5}, {"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 3}], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800072413413508", "filename": "OST-250827.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 2082545, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800072413413508/OST-250827.jpg?ex=69cccffc&is=69cb7e7c&hm=11654e6c42cde5197afebe0b1aedca6a1114adc102a1531f37c390617df3b4de&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438800308263452752", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**01. 欢迎来到万象旅店！-Welcome to Cosmic Tavern! -**\n\n这里是位于异世界时空裂隙之中的万象旅店。\n连接着不同宇宙的传送门，闪烁着浩瀚的星光，欢迎着你的到来。\n等等……这是给咱守密人干哪儿来了？\n\nThis is the Cosmic Tavern, located in the spatial rift of another universe.\nThe portal connecting different universes shimmers with the vast starlight, welcoming your arrival.\nWait a minute... Where on earth are we?", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T07:58:45.107000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800307520798862", "filename": "1.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1363692, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800307520798862/1.jpg?ex=69ccd034&is=69cb7eb4&hm=36c2daa4f2ff6d3b7005c9545528ac5be02fc1c36ac91364397ce0cf6638f7ae&"}, {"id": "1438800307869061151", "filename": "01._-Welcome_to_Cosmic_Tavern_-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 23586164, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800307869061151/01._-Welcome_to_Cosmic_Tavern_-.wav?ex=69ccd035&is=69cb7eb5&hm=4a728f97a50cfc12bf27b5efa945ace16a84e2a7d8b9ff7e92d4482212fcb2d2&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438800445530308649", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**02. 老板娘，伊格娜蒂丝！-Tavern Keeper，Ignatiss! -**\n\n“快来跟我签订契约，成为卡牌大师吧！”\n这位来自异世界的龙族美少女向你发出了热情而莫名其妙的邀请。\n为了让这个相位空间的小意外尽快回复正常，你别无选择。\n\n\"Come sign a contract with me and become a Card Master!\"\nThis dragon maiden from another world extends an enthusiastic yet baffling invitation to you.\nTo quickly resolve this Phase Space anomaly, you have no choice but to comply.", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T07:59:17.834000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800444578336829", "filename": "02._-Tavern_KeeperIgnatiss_-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 16742106, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800444578336829/02._-Tavern_KeeperIgnatiss_-.wav?ex=69ccd055&is=69cb7ed5&hm=3f1774c58b494b724d234e75fdc94f57d7bfa33b713153b6e46718e139a11c80&"}, {"id": "1438800445089779863", "filename": "2.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1367892, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800445089779863/2.jpg?ex=69ccd055&is=69cb7ed5&hm=a8b1cc74201921eebbd649c7fedc96cb82ae46c6d762c0bfe77bbe52590bf9c7&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438800570415714364", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**03. 无限续杯！-Unlimited refills!-**\n\n一千颗橡果的故事，总要由第一颗开始。\n在相位对弈中，你每打出一张卡牌，\n伊格娜蒂丝的眸中便莫名掠过一缕金色的回忆流光。\n\nThe story of a thousand acorns must always begin with the first one.\nIn Traphase, each time you play a card, a glimmer of golden memory flits in Ignatiss's eyes.", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T07:59:47.609000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800569807536148", "filename": "3.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1337394, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800569807536148/3.jpg?ex=69ccd073&is=69cb7ef3&hm=6e03c5b7aeb32d9c17c50629318ec01c626e6b290406111040cd291202055a61&"}, {"id": "1438800570113855598", "filename": "03._-Unlimited_refills-.mp3", "content_type": "audio/mpeg", "size": 6968640, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800570113855598/03._-Unlimited_refills-.mp3?ex=69ccd073&is=69cb7ef3&hm=12d8dab6478cdae7b2f0ea0ebcd917c2ce02e34235e178420ab122da4cb44208&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438800678695866399", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**04. 一起来玩万象牌吧！-Let's play Cosmic Card!-**\n\n“每日试训没有做？不如先来一盘万象牌吧！”\n“融灾禁区没有打？不如先来一盘万象牌吧！”\n“这是相位对弈，不是万象牌！一千颗橡果我会收集给你看的！”\n\n\"Haven't completed your Daily Quest? How about a round of Cosmic Cards instead?\"\n\"Haven't cleared the D-Effect Zone? How about a round of Cosmic Cards instead?\"\n\"This is Traphase, not Cosmic Cards! I'll gather 1000 acorns, just you watch!\"", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T08:00:13.425000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800677559341206", "filename": "04._-Lets_play_Cosmic_Card-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 18902108, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800677559341206/04._-Lets_play_Cosmic_Card-.wav?ex=69ccd08d&is=69cb7f0d&hm=3413c7e73e95989b746a4c4317108e69369ba5388c47c0155a32088527894552&"}, {"id": "1438800678293340280", "filename": "4.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1354750, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800678293340280/4.jpg?ex=69ccd08d&is=69cb7f0d&hm=37666f6a6f5ccc6792cb58f56b93ad611ae2672dc3bad711d89350ed61ddce5b&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438800905121300530", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**05. 属于我的逆转时刻！-It's My Turn!-**\n\n尽管局面对你不利，但你的嘴角已经微微扬起。\n“我的回合，抽卡！”\n不管是在万象旅店还是在弥萨格，\n小看辅助的伤害能力可都是要吃大亏的啊！伊格娜蒂丝！\n\nDespite the unfavorable situation, a faint smile curls at the corner of your lips.\n\"It's my turn to draw!\"\nWhether at the Cosmic Tavern or in Mythag, underestimating the damage capability of a support will cost you dearly, Ignatiss!", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T08:01:07.409000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438800904433438802", "filename": "5.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1351186, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800904433438802/5.jpg?ex=69ccd0c3&is=69cb7f43&hm=da66cc88a05e6857a06c3b94861653d47e8db2cd3a1cb647d472bfcba34e129d&"}, {"id": "1438800904777109534", "filename": "05._-Its_My_Turn-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 19016032, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438800904777109534/05._-Its_My_Turn-.wav?ex=69ccd0c3&is=69cb7f43&hm=6a8add5b341f83c87bf0b7302fa8834c5f9962d49a31be2a87ad7e9305e6db29&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438801091893657621", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**06. 弥萨格利刃！-Mythag's Blade!-**\n\n弥萨格的利刃会为你取得这场对弈的胜利。\n你和搭档之间的羁绊坚不可摧。\n哪怕你们有一天身处于不同宇宙，也一定无法改变这一点。\n\nMythag's Blade will secure your victory in this duel.\nThe bond between you and your partner is unbreakable.\nThis will never change, even if you find yourselves in different universes one day.", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T08:01:51.939000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438801090983231518", "filename": "06._-Mythags_Blade-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 30422980, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438801090983231518/06._-Mythags_Blade-.wav?ex=69ccd0ef&is=69cb7f6f&hm=2a3cf4c2503ae7483ece5a79bebb82ed2dd829b602a33268becca20a237ffda6&"}, {"id": "1438801091566374955", "filename": "6.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1348483, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438801091566374955/6.jpg?ex=69ccd0ef&is=69cb7f6f&hm=9a90629b56ed8c5a12c9811d98c9fc3407cfa07be3d19d48b10a672a24770931&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
{"id": "1438801175473426533", "channel_id": "1438800071977078814", "type": 0, "author_id": "1131790839291596841", "author_name": "morimensstaff01", "author_bot": false, "content": "**07. 再见了，卡牌大师！-Goodbye Card Master!-**\n\n这片破碎的时空裂隙之中曾经坐落着传说中的万象旅店。\n曾经连接着不同宇宙的传送门，曾经闪烁着浩瀚的星光，曾经欢迎着每一位卡牌大师的到来。\n而你，是这一切存在过的证明。\n\nWithin this shattered spatial rift once stood the legendary Cosmic Tavern.\nThe portals connecting different universes once shimmered with the vast starlight, welcoming the arrival of every Card Master.\nAnd you are the proof that all of this once existed.", "timestamp": "2025-11-14T08:02:11.866000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1438801174651473972", "filename": "7.jpg", "content_type": "image/jpeg", "size": 1345537, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438801174651473972/7.jpg?ex=69ccd103&is=69cb7f83&hm=8a4a013b739ce1bfc8bbae172a170a854c74d201132fcbb4c925c91fb9d3ea9b&"}, {"id": "1438801175188344935", "filename": "07._-Goodbye_Card_Master-.wav", "content_type": "audio/x-wav", "size": 23722060, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1438800071977078814/1438801175188344935/07._-Goodbye_Card_Master-.wav?ex=69ccd103&is=69cb7f83&hm=d1a73e76b3f0b7634a8179186ebdfcf01914a542918d835ee15d14107db9c656&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1438800071977078814", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "忘却前夜OST：逆转回合EP·万象旅店的回响", "forum_channel_id": "1181146813890302033", "thread_tags": ["1229389668261564426"]}
